reviews.review_text: I agree with the liner notes - Nice FOB That said, I took a quick listen to the SBD and found it also very listenable with the vocal mics not overly hot, as is sometimes the case.  This FOB recording has more high end and is punchier than Weinberg's source.   With the board, the two together would make an awesome matrix.
Killer '81 Agree with Lilrich - bring on the Mtx. I think this source actually has better pitch & body than the others as of 4/18.  Had this source on tape & still prefer it.
